<!DOCTYPE concept PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD DITA Concept//EN" "concept.dtd">
<concept id="concept_dzn_cdy_1cb">
 <title>Update DPM On-premises</title>
 <shortdesc>If you use <ph
            conref="../Reusable_Content/ReusablePhrases.dita#concept_vhs_5tz_xp/DPM-short"/>
        on-premises and you upgrade registered <ph
            conref="../Reusable_Content/ReusablePhrases.dita#concept_vhs_5tz_xp/pName-long"/>s to a
        version higher than your current version of <ph
            conref="../Reusable_Content/ReusablePhrases.dita#concept_vhs_5tz_xp/DPM-short"/>, you
        must modify the <ph
            conref="../Reusable_Content/ReusablePhrases.dita#concept_vhs_5tz_xp/pName-long"/>
        version range within your <ph
            conref="../Reusable_Content/ReusablePhrases.dita#concept_vhs_5tz_xp/DPM-short"/>
        installation.</shortdesc>
 <conbody>
        <p>By default, <ph
                conref="../Reusable_Content/ReusablePhrases.dita#concept_vhs_5tz_xp/DPM-short"/> can
            work with registered <ph
                conref="../Reusable_Content/ReusablePhrases.dita#concept_vhs_5tz_xp/pName-long"/>s
            from version 2.1.0.0 to the current version of <ph
                conref="../Reusable_Content/ReusablePhrases.dita#concept_vhs_5tz_xp/DPM-short"/>.
            You can customize the <ph
                conref="../Reusable_Content/ReusablePhrases.dita#concept_vhs_5tz_xp/pName-long"/>
            version range. For example, if you use <ph
                conref="../Reusable_Content/ReusablePhrases.dita#concept_vhs_5tz_xp/DPM-short"/>
            on-premises version 2.7.2 and you upgrade registered <ph
                conref="../Reusable_Content/ReusablePhrases.dita#concept_vhs_5tz_xp/pName-long"/>s
            to version <ph
                conref="../Reusable_Content/ReusablePhrases.dita#concept_vhs_5tz_xp/version"/>, you
            must configure the maximum <ph
                conref="../Reusable_Content/ReusablePhrases.dita#concept_vhs_5tz_xp/pName-long"/>
            version that can work with <ph
                conref="../Reusable_Content/ReusablePhrases.dita#concept_vhs_5tz_xp/DPM-short"/> to
            version <ph conref="../Reusable_Content/ReusablePhrases.dita#concept_vhs_5tz_xp/version"
            />.</p>
        <p>To modify the <ph
                conref="../Reusable_Content/ReusablePhrases.dita#concept_vhs_5tz_xp/pName-long"/>
            version range:</p>
  <p>
            <ol id="ol_xbl_f2y_1cb">
                <li>Log in to <ph
                        conref="../Reusable_Content/ReusablePhrases.dita#concept_vhs_5tz_xp/DPM-short"
                    /> as the default system administrator - the admin@admin user account.</li>
                <li>In the Navigation panel, click <menucascade>
                        <uicontrol>Administration</uicontrol>
                        <uicontrol>Data Collectors</uicontrol>
                    </menucascade>.</li>
                <li>Click the <uicontrol>Component Version Range</uicontrol> icon: <image
                        href="../Graphics/icon_OrganizationConfig.png" scale="70"
                        id="image_hd3_dfy_1cb"/>.</li>
                <li>Enter <ph
                        conref="../Reusable_Content/ReusablePhrases.dita#concept_vhs_5tz_xp/version"
                    /> as the maximum <ph
                        conref="../Reusable_Content/ReusablePhrases.dita#concept_vhs_5tz_xp/pName-long"
                    /> version that can work with <ph
                        conref="../Reusable_Content/ReusablePhrases.dita#concept_vhs_5tz_xp/DPM-short"
                    />.</li>
            </ol>
        </p>
 </conbody>
</concept>
